						               													<description>Flume is an extremely simple game for two players.  Start with a Go board lined with a perimeter of green stones (painted on).  The players, Red and Blue, take turns adding stones of their own color.  If you add a stone which forms 3 or 4 connections (orthogonal adjacencies) with neighboring stones of any color (red, blue or green) add another stone while it's still your turn.  And so on.  Your turn concludes when you add a stone which forms 2 or less connections with neighboring stones.  The object is to have the most stones on the board after it has been filled with stones.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Flume gameplay is strongly related to Dots and Boxes gameplay.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
